ENCAPSULATION:
   creating a variable & Method -> within the boundaries of a class
    Data Hiding {Variable Hiding}
    make variables private
    and access this private variables through setter and getter method

    1) private variable, public method [setter & getter method] => Use setter for non-mandatory + mutable data
    2) private variable, constructor   => Use constructors for mandatory data and non-mutable data [jis data ko kabhi change nhi karna hai]


     Rules to use Constructor
       -setting multiple values at one and same time
       -setting values of mandatory fields
       -setting values of non-mutable fields

     Rules for Setter method
       -setting one value at a time
       -setting values of non-mandatory fields
       -setting values of mutable fields


     Constructor + Setter
        -setting value though constructor
        -updating value through setter


     3) private methods encapsulated within public method